{"tid":407562,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[日經] 問絲打 病左果時聽到啲咩說話會覺得受安慰","createTime":"2017-09-20T13:44:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T00:03:18.000Z","uid":5944,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"d85dc58d30b374797c4fc896a814e9d139480c80","tid":407562,"uid":5944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:44:03.000Z","msg":"我已經講左好多次<br />\n買野上黎比你食 早啲休息 有冇食藥 飲多啲水 快啲返屋企休息 <br />\n<br />\n我真係盡左力 但條女都覺得佢想人氹果時冇人氹佢<br />\n我應該講啲咩 有冇例句參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba3e1bb44be47c7fa3b244c719db64b1f0e49aa","tid":407562,"uid":74764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:45:26.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢"},{"pid":"02b17f5fb127db2d47459005ffbe0f960ce4f411","tid":407562,"uid":5944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:46:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名學嘢</blockquote><br />\n快撚啲學呀 如果唔係好似我宜家咁 就散架喇<br />\n我真係已經好撚盡力關心佢"},{"pid":"f09dec7d4f31b94c2bdb9c637af2aae4afe220fa","tid":407562,"uid":117032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:47:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名學嘢</blockquote><br />\n快撚啲學呀 如果唔係好似我宜家咁 就散架喇<br />\n我真係已經好撚盡力關心佢</blockquote><br />\n留名睇分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b86f4b75b9389778cfc0af5bc67a9b21708021","tid":407562,"uid":142039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:48:53.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86324f8a1f615f5688f86be673d6370ace1b0ce","tid":407562,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:49:06.000Z","msg":"其實病咗嚟嚟去去都係講呢啲嘢㗎啦 仲可以講咩啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b7dfecb792f1d4c0744b3ae291597e8033d04d","tid":407562,"uid":139763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:49:56.000Z","msg":"請快啲好番"},{"pid":"a29fda613c6bed76b728872c03c44f97a1d700b4","tid":407562,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:50:27.000Z","msg":"問佢幾時大殮"},{"pid":"e04c47e145d4156954aaecac7c7c8de2312da107","tid":407562,"uid":99051,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:51:05.000Z","msg":"講多錯多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  注意係病個時一定唔可以開玩笑"},{"pid":"29a294d57dde3dd8087bfb6f9577bcbecafd887c","tid":407562,"uid":17402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:52:34.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗幫你打支發燒針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f9d26541a6a9f0c545e1642ed5b026ba53e6c5","tid":407562,"uid":99051,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :好返我帶你去食（xxx) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 好呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5dd58ad85c684aae75b74e38a49985abfa7f96","tid":407562,"uid":20423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:52:50.000Z","msg":"你覺得點阿/係咪好辛苦阿 etc<br />\n有時親自買碗粥上佢屋企好過剩係靠講"},{"pid":"e74a337b67abfdf80f6bece187b54858fa2a2249","tid":407562,"uid":5944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:53:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實病咗嚟嚟去去都係講呢啲嘢㗎啦 仲可以講咩啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢仲要摷返前幾日比佢陰我單野話我唔關心佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢果晚十點幾十一點話想執房 問我想唔想幫手<br />\n我問聽日得唔得<br />\n佢就話咁我宜家執喇<br />\n<br />\n隔左陣屌鳩我唔幫佢搬櫃 搞到佢要自己搬 覺得自己好似冇男朋友咁<br />\n然後咁岩又唔舒服 就賴埋話因為搬櫃太攰所以發燒<br />\n<br />\n大佬我點知你既執房係要將啲櫃搬黎搬去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我平時幫人補習唔會禁電話 廢事收人錢但咁唔專心<br />\n今日都唔想佢病仲唔覆佢 覺得無助 我已經照覆機<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bedf0040b16798acaaeab8de76f182652698fdde","tid":407562,"uid":55296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:53:59.000Z","msg":"話 我陪住你 唔洗擔心 好快無事 辛苦多一陣 已經好好<br />\n又燥又病心情都唔多好㗎喇 唔好講埋啲懶搞笑嘅嘢"},{"pid":"97977ac6fcd2b32525169309afdb84cadf2211c0","tid":407562,"uid":82398,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:54:00.000Z","msg":"你唔係佢想要既人點哄都無用"},{"pid":"ad16f7189a10f34df603eecb4bc522a9852c9458","tid":407562,"uid":117032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:54:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗唔洗幫你打支發燒針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n發燒針定退燒針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d00479d9b7751d1b7e3e22f59bec2a9975563d6","tid":407562,"uid":5944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:56:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你覺得點阿/係咪好辛苦阿 etc<br />\n有時親自買碗粥上佢屋企好過剩係靠講</blockquote><br />\n問題係佢都唔係屋企 我可以點買野比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以前都有買粥上去比以前既女朋友食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過如果咁講仲死啦 佢覺得我以前錫女朋友宜家唔錫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4872b85fa214211bf6bbd2e048bb1ebac5eebb","tid":407562,"uid":5944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T14:14:56.000Z","msg":"推呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"83322d48aba93faaaba45a3162f4f45d0009fce8","tid":407562,"uid":136582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T14:37:26.000Z","msg":"我無比你病 你唔可以病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7b9cca1e428c038782ee5514c13daaa008336b","tid":407562,"uid":11776,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T14:47:10.000Z","msg":"氹到咁都唔中意，你條女想點呀<br />\n如果我條仔肯安慰我一句，肯定係佢食錯藥"},{"pid":"30c0b14f11904ca480497ed4ae918f034218e73e","tid":407562,"uid":80661,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T14:49:17.000Z","msg":"攬住佢就得<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"971c8948bf2bb3a6b55814d352c0c13ae13d4e4a","tid":407562,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T14:49:55.000Z","msg":"死得未？"},{"pid":"93f76cc3493759e8f8c750c6c3db0a2da0bd718f","tid":407562,"uid":5944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T15:15:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死得未？</blockquote><br />\n我死得 好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69fbc45eb1128eff1e82eb8bc68ac92f61694663","tid":407562,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T15:15:38.000Z","msg":"幫你奶"},{"pid":"535c38d513d14fe7cc5a8b4c8aa2abed3abaf778","tid":407562,"uid":135668,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T15:58:08.000Z","msg":"屌病撚左仲咁撚多野搞  係病嘅就抖多啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   比着我病我男朋友是但講句安慰說話已經好滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}